body:
I’m beginning to see Shen falling off much harder than the other tanks who has nothing really to abuse in their kit in the current meta compared to someone like Maokai (the other top lane tank I enjoy playing frequently)…

Shen or Maokai from now? I want on primary tank so I don’t really wanna play both so I can focus on one. I’m currently leaning towards Maokai at the moment as Shen just seems underwhelming in terms of how much protection he can grant for his carries compared to the AoE 20% damage reduction with Maokai…

